getRelationshipTypes

ItemToItemRelationshipTypes getRelationshipTypes(boolean parent)
                                                 throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Returns a collection of ItemToItemRelationshipType objects that represent defined item to item relationship types for this item type.

Parameters:
parent - indicates the direction of the relationship. If parent is set to true, the list of relationship types in which this item type appears as a Parent (From) node is returned. If parent is set to false, the list of relationship types in which this item type appears as a Child (To) node is returned.
Returns:
a collection of ItemToItemRelationshipType objects.
Throws:
DimensionsRuntimeException - if connection error or internal error occurs
